    "description": "踏上一个激动人心的回合制策略海盗游戏之旅，巧妙地融合了roguelike元素与激烈的竞技场海战。做出关键决策，适应不断变化的情况，并在每一次转折中智胜敌人。指挥你的船只穿越激烈的战斗，成为最终的海盗冠军。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/c6ba4f615d52ffda86f26f7bf13f4741.webp?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.poster.avif?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.webm?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/eb7e4f9746bca50eb9d01f19a4665d62.mp4?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 同时执行动作以进行战略预测和定位。<br></li><li> 导航障碍并利用环境为己所用。<br></li><li> 利用风来减少顺风航行时的移动成本，避开风暴或利用风暴逃避追击的玩家。<br></li><li> 恐惧不断增长的海洋诅咒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/6e271bd38df06e7289a521a734512ef4.webp?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.poster.avif?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.webm?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/0fbcb34dd737527d6b69fb18b7c2d362.mp4?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 选择各种升级以增加你的力量。<br></li><li> 释放环境混乱，给七海带来灾难，给你带来优势和劣势。<br></li><li> 通过选择具有更大力量的特殊神话技能来引导战斗的方向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/2f320a51f8b666169365b51387a4ad28.webp?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.poster.avif?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.webm?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/405353f2d53ca9a32894a87b9d210b88.mp4?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 管理你的船员，给他们分配钓鱼、寻宝和资源收集等任务。<br></li><li> 升级你的船只并定制组件，以增加航行速度、更强的防御、更好的视野和更快的维修速度。<br></li><li> 在你的舰队中选择并扮演一个角色，并为一支强大的船员贡献力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/c1e7bd29249dfe520af6ca459c672baa.webp?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.poster.avif?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.webm?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/7ae42e607b28440921f83e1fc61fbc04.mp4?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 挑战史诗级boss，获得他们的力量，并解锁能力以造成混乱。<br></li><li> 与海怪战斗，获得宝贵的升级和显著的增益。<br></li><li> 击败AI舰队和强大的海盗船，或邀请他们在好的交易中与你并肩作战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/1c290342890577bfec09ccf2dadcd2b2.webp?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/17abe9d9f84a59d3a6d10154e3dda310.poster.avif?t=1758134168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/17abe9d9f84a59d3a6d10154e3dda310.webm?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014870/extras/17abe9d9f84a59d3a6d10154e3dda310.mp4?t=1758134168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 参与自由战、合作战和团队战等游戏模式。<br></li><li> 通过与技能水平相当的对手匹配来提升ELO排名。<br><br></li></ul>",
